Reasoning: 
1) cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with medical lesion detection using deep learning techniques. 
2) cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper introduces a novel network architecture for medical lesion detection. 
3) cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the application of AI in medical imaging. 
4) cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with medical image analysis. 
5) cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the problem of lack of annotations for all types of lesions and proposes a solution using a relation transfer module.
